reviews.title: game for preteens w/no social skills
reviews.comment: This game is very sexist. And not only that but, teaches young people to play games with guys. And to cause scenes. Which is bad since THIS GAME IS TO HELP PRETEENS WITH NO SOCIAL SKILLS WHATSOEVER (any one with any social skills will know right answers. Except a lot of these are WRONG & sexist.) However, i applaud that they teach safety issues, BUT if they are teaching that why would they assume it\'s ok to teach sexual things to young people...? I am uninstalling.
